And how does a mendicant accomplished in proper attention develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path
Its when a mendicant develops right view right thought right speech right action right livelihood right effort right mindfulness and right immersion which culminate in the removal of greed hate and delusion
Thats how a mendicant accomplished in proper attention develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path
