What seven
They attain enlightenment early on in this very life
If not they attain enlightenment at the time of death
If not with the ending of the five lower fetters theyre extinguished between one life and the next 
theyre extinguished upon landing 
theyre extinguished without extra effort 
theyre extinguished with extra effort 
they head upstream going to the Akaniṭṭha realm
