Which is more the two or three drops drawn out or the water in the ocean
Sir the water in the ocean is certainly more
The two or three drops drawn out are tiny
Compared to the water in the ocean its not nearly a hundredth a thousandth or a hundred thousandth part
In the same way for a noble disciple the suffering thats over and done with is more 
