More than ninety laymen in Nādika have passed away having ended three fetters and weakened greed hate and delusion Theyre oncereturners who will come back to this world once only then make an end of suffering
In excess of five hundred laymen in Nādika have passed away having ended three fetters Theyre streamenterers not liable to be reborn in the underworld bound for awakening
Its hardly surprising that a human being should pass away
But if you should come and ask me about it each and every time someone passes away that would be a bother for me
